const aboutContent = `
# About Law & Associates

Founded in 1998, Law & Associates has been a cornerstone of legal excellence in our community for over 25 years. Our firm was built on the principles of integrity, dedication, and unwavering commitment to our clients' success.

## Our Mission

We are committed to providing exceptional legal services with personalized attention to every client. Our goal is to make the legal process as smooth and understandable as possible while achieving the best possible outcomes for our clients.

## Our Values

- **Integrity**: We maintain the highest ethical standards in all our dealings
- **Excellence**: We strive for excellence in every case we handle
- **Compassion**: We understand that legal matters can be stressful and provide compassionate support
- **Innovation**: We stay current with legal developments and technology to serve our clients better
`;

const teamContent = `
## Our Legal Team

Our attorneys bring together decades of combined experience across multiple practice areas. Each team member is dedicated to providing personalized, effective legal representation.
`;

const historyContent = `
## Our History

### 1998 - Foundation
Law & Associates was founded by John Smith and Sarah Johnson with a vision to provide accessible, high-quality legal services to individuals and businesses.

### 2005 - Expansion
The firm expanded to include specialized practice areas in real estate and business law, growing our team to 10 attorneys.

### 2015 - Technology Integration
We embraced modern technology to improve client communication and case management, making our services more efficient and accessible.

### 2024 - Continued Growth
Today, we serve clients across multiple states with a team of 25+ attorneys and support staff, maintaining our commitment to personalized service.
`;
